{"about_the_game":"Mutant scum never learn! Blaster Master Zero makes its Steam debut!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBlaster Master Zero is a 8-bit style top-down &amp; sideview 2D action-adventure game that hearkens back to the golden age of the NES.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis game was created using the original 1988 title &quot;Blaster Master&quot; from Sunsoft as a base, with the addition of new areas and bosses, new gameplay elements such as extra sub-weapons, improved gameplay, a more robust scenario, refined and expanded exploration mechanics, and more.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbOn the sideview maps, take control of the battle tank SOPHIA III and explore your surroundings as you search for the entrance to the dungeon where the area's boss lurks.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbOnce you find a dungeon entrance, exit SOPHIA III and make your way inside as the hero Jason and take on the mutants that dwell within in top-down mode.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbDefeat the mid-bosses and area bosses to acquire new items, sub-weapons, upgrades to SOPHIA III and Jason's equipment, and new abilities and maneuvers that allow SOPHIA III to access new areas.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u30fbPlayer 2 can provide support for Player 1 as they traverse through the game in the co-op multiplayer mode.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"MEMORIES OF THE METAFIGHT","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1034900/4cfddb9b6d0c0fd37c50442493844da8b94076e1.jpg"},{"name":"EVE'SDECEPTION","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1034900/94096642479db59e22ed12af46769ba1537c7240.jpg"},{"name":"THE FOREST DESTROYER","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1034900/2e57d4159c07a427c833405360c51527ff9ea770.jpg"},{"name":"THE TOXIC VERMIN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1034900/5b3c1ce1026c9beac1885a95312dec7316acce42.jpg"},{"name":"THE UNCONTROLLABLE\u3000ENGINE","pat